ctre
------------------------------------------
Fast compile-time regular expressions with support for
matching/searching/capturing during compile-time or runtime.

Runtime requirements:
  pkg-config-2.5.1-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  binutils-2.46.1-1
  cmake-4.2.1-1
  cygport-0.37.7-1
  gcc-core-14.4.0-1
  gcc-g++-14.4.0-1
  ninja-1.13.2-1

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/hanickadot/compile-time-regular-expressions

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/hanickadot/compile-time-regular-expressions/archive/refs/tags/v3.11.0.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack ctre-3.11.0-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./ctre-3.11.0-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/ctre-3.11.0-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/ctre-3.11.0-X.tar.xz

